a JBoss file descriptor named jboss-web.xml in /WebContent/WEB-INF/ directory;

The schema definition file for jboss-web.xml is named jboss-web_8_0.xsd and can be
located in the JBOSS_HOME/docs/schema folder.

 создание jboss-web.xml делает приложение не переносным для других
Серверы приложений Java EE.

right-clicking on
the Eclipse Server tab and selecting Add and Remove.

click on Add to add the project to the list of configured resources on the server

f you have started WildFly from inside Eclipse, the resource will be automatically
deployed by checking the flag to see whether the server has started, and publish changes
immediately
